<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <div class="section-tag" data-num="01">Who I Am</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Statistician. Analyst.<br/>Data Engineer in progress.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">A rigorous blend of academic excellence and real-world analytical practice.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-body reveal-left">
      <p>
        I'm a statistician and data analyst with a <strong>First-Class BSc (4.61/5.00)</strong> from the University of Abuja, 
        currently completing my <strong>MSc in Statistics at the University of Ibadan</strong> — one of Africa's foremost 
        research institutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        My expertise spans <strong>statistical modelling, machine learning, research methodology, and data analysis</strong>. 
        I've applied these skills across academic, corporate, and consultancy settings using R, Python, 
        SPSS, EViews, and Excel. I'm now expanding into SQL and data engineering to build end-to-end pipelines.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've co-authored <strong>3 peer-reviewed journal publications</strong> in public health and epidemiology, 
        and actively take on research and data projects for academic and corporate clients.
